review.name: Don't book with this company. Terrible experience - untrustworthy
review.reviewBody: Do not book with this company. I booked a return transfer and they cancelled the transfer without personally notifying me. Turns out they had a price change and did not want to honour the original cost. You don't want an unethical and dishonest company bailing out on you at the last minute (judging from the previous review), or randomly exiting out of an agreed contract (through Viator) because they suddenly decided to increase their prices.

review.name: Incomplete, very dissatisfied and disappointed.
review.reviewBody:
I made and paid for my reservation for the beginning of May, 2022 from Seattle airport to our Hotel and back to the airport the next week.
I got a text as soon as we landed, confirming that my driver was on his way.   
When I got out of baggage claim, I headed to the pick-up area.  I waited and finally called them.  A lady, who refused to identify herself told me that the driver had "overextended himself and can't pick you up".  I asked her about my return trip and she suggested I find another means of getting back to the airport.  She assured me my payment would be refunded in 3 to 5 days.  After 9 days, I filed a complaint with my credit card company.  Extremely disappointed to be stranded at the Seattle airport.  I'm very thankful for the wonderful taxi service that we used though.  They were very helpful and picked us up within a few minutes.

review.name: B-day Seattle
review.reviewBody: Kinfu, our driver was the best…almost no wait time and he was very professional even offering places to eat and see that was walkable from our hotel.

itemListElement.name: Celebrate with a Holiday Scavenger Hunt in Seattle with Holly Jolly Hunt

name: Celebrate with a Holiday Scavenger Hunt in Seattle with Holly Jolly Hunt
description: Celebrate the magic of the season this year with Holly Jolly Hunt. Holly Jolly Hunt is an app based scavenger hunt that you can play anywhere of your choosing. Explore the city and look for holiday related items, both traditional and not so traditional. Take a photo through the app to score points for your scavenger hunt team. Perform fun, holiday challenges that will bring laughter to your team. See your score on the leaderboard compared to other teams from all over. Holly Jolly Hunt is guaranteed to provide lasting holiday memories. Whether you play with friends, family, or even co-workers, Holly Jolly will put a smile on your face for the rest of the year!
